(457, 'Florence Welch', '1986-08-28', NULL, 1, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/abmRByJsQPsYgkD0Z6waLfPnk4u.jpg', 'Florence Leontine Mary Welch (born 28 August 1986) is an English musician, singer and songwriter from London. She is best known as the lead vocalist and songwriter of the indie rock band Florence and the Machine. The band\'s music is renowned for its dramatic and eccentric production and also Welch\'s powerful vocal performances.'),
