(687, 'Lucy Hale', '1989-06-14', 'Memphis, Tennessee, USA', 1, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/r3hs2FTSp0RvR7lB2jeqF6tNg9z.jpg', 'Karen Lucille Hale (born June 14, 1989), better known as Lucy Hale, is an American actress and singer. She is known for her roles as Becca Sommers in Bionic Woman, Rose Baker in Privileged, Sherrie in the horror film Scream 4, and as Aria Montgomery on the hit ABC Family series Pretty Little Liars. She is also known for her appearance on the reality show American Juniors.\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Lucy Hale, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia'),
(688, 'Tyler Posey', '1991-10-18', 'Santa Monica, California, USA', 2, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4yQTHc4pofc1j3doHRDBwuSpJ2w.jpg', 'Tyler Garcia Posey (born October 18, 1991) is an American actor, musician, and producer. He is best known for his role as Scott McCall in Teen Wolf.'),
