(38, '千と千尋の神隠し', '2001-07-20', 'A young girl, Chihiro, becomes trapped in a strange new world of spirits. When her parents undergo a mysterious transformation, she must call upon the courage she never knew she had to free her family.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dL11DBPcRhWWnJcFXl9A07MrqTI.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ByXuk9QqQkk', 125, 8.40, NULL, 26.815696),
(39, 'Despicable Me 2', '2013-06-25', 'Gru is recruited by the Anti-Villain League to help deal with a powerful new super criminal.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kQrYyZQHkwkUg2KlUDyvymj9FAp.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TlbnGSMJQbQ', 98, 6.90, 'PG', 26.636256),
(40, 'Kung Fu Panda', '2008-06-04', 'When the Valley of Peace is threatened, lazy Po the panda discovers his destiny as the \"chosen one\" and trains to become a kung fu hero, but transforming the unsleek slacker into a brave warrior won\'t be easy. It\'s up to Master Shifu and the Furious Five -- Tigress, Crane, Mantis, Viper and Monkey -- to give it a try.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2Paj1nufT0jeSY0G4u3RC31HIGT.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PXi3Mv6KMzY', 90, 7.00, 'PG', 26.294542),
(41, 'Ice Age: Dawn of the Dinosaurs', '2009-06-29', 'Times are changing for Manny the moody mammoth, Sid the motor mouthed sloth and Diego the crafty saber-toothed tiger. Life heats up for our heroes when they meet some new and none-too-friendly neighbors – the mighty dinosaurs.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/crAf8b9gFpcdvY7majL8xWzTbem.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dP-xFvTIdNk', 94, 6.50, 'PG', 26.135684),
(42, 'Up', '2009-05-13', 'Carl Fredricksen spent his entire life dreaming of exploring the globe and experiencing life to its fullest. But at age 78, life seems to have passed him by, until a twist of fate (and a persistent 8-year old Wilderness Explorer named Russell) gives him a new lease on life.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nk11pvocdb5zbFhX5oq5YiLPYMo.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ORFWdXl_zJ4', 96, 7.80, 'PG', 25.781873),
(43, 'Jumanji: Welcome to the Jungle', '2017-12-09', 'The tables are turned as four teenagers are sucked into Jumanji\'s world - pitted against rhinos, black mambas and an endless variety of jungle traps and puzzles. To survive, they\'ll play as characters from the game.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bXrZ5iHBEjH7WMidbUDQ0U2xbmr.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2QKg5SZ_35I', 119, 6.60, 'PG-13', 56.081347),
(44, 'Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles', '2014-08-07', 'The city needs heroes. Darkness has settled over New York City as Shredder and his evil Foot Clan have an iron grip on everything from the police to the politicians. The future is grim until four unlikely outcast brothers rise from the sewers and discover their destiny as Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles. The Turtles must work with fearless reporter April and her wise-cracking cameraman Vern Fenwick to save the city and unravel Shredder\'s diabolical plan.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oDL2ryJ0sV2bmjgshVgJb3qzvwp.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dwXFsrp6WBs', 101, 5.80, 'PG-13', 45.659824),
